{"title":"WTC Doubles Down on Ultraviolet Purple, Standard Purple Fades Away","link":"https://bikerumor.com/wtc-ultraviolet-purple-bike-parts/","date":1739464447000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-whole-group-2.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" alt=\"(Photo / Wolf Tooth Components)\" /></p>\n<p>Recently, If you’ve been on the Wolf Tooth Components website, you may have noticed two different anodized purple variants. The “standard purple” as it is now known, has been around since WTC started anodizing color options. That OG purple is now being replaced with a new-school color with old-school inspiration: Ultraviolet Purple.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Components-Ultraviolet-Purple-waveform-pedals.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Components-Ultraviolet-Purple-waveform-pedals.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components Ultraviolet Purple waveform pedals\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Components-Ultraviolet-Purple-waveform-pedals.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Components-Ultraviolet-Purple-waveform-pedals-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Components-Ultraviolet-Purple-waveform-pedals-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Components-Ultraviolet-Purple-waveform-pedals-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Components-Ultraviolet-Purple-waveform-pedals-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Components-Ultraviolet-Purple-waveform-pedals-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Wolf Tooth Components)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The response to the Ultraviolet Purple has been overwhelmingly positive since it first appeared on the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-components-wtc-waveform-flat-pedal/\" target=\"_blank\">Waveform Aluminum Pedals</a> back in 2022. It’s bright and vibrant. And purple!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-top-cap-2.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-top-cap-2.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Ultra Violet Purple headset top cap 2\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-top-cap-2.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-top-cap-2-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-top-cap-2-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-top-cap-2-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-top-cap-2-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-top-cap-2-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-2.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-2.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Ultra Violet Purple headset 2\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-2.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-2-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-2-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-2-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-2-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-2-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>WTC’s new Ultraviolet purple will be available on headsets, grip collars, seatpost clamps, center lock rotor lockrings, headset spacers, alloy bar end plugs, ReMote levers, and anything else on <a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/collections/color-shop-purple/?gf_515667=Purple\" target=\"_blank\">this page</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-center-lock-2.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-center-lock-2.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Ultra Violet Purple center lock 2\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-center-lock-2.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-center-lock-2-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-center-lock-2-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-center-lock-2-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-center-lock-2-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-center-lock-2-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Visit Wolf Tooth Components and take a gander at the new Purple bits available. Plus, while there, check out all the other beautiful parts available.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-close-up-2.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-close-up-2.webp\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Ultra Violet Purple headset close up 2\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-close-up-2.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-close-up-2-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-close-up-2-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-close-up-2-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-close-up-2-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Wolf-Tooth-Ultra-Violet-Purple-headset-close-up-2-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WolfToothComponents.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wtc-ultraviolet-purple-bike-parts/\">WTC Doubles Down on Ultraviolet Purple, Standard Purple Fades Away</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"0be54c1d4db08a5696171b8b8cc5ae3b4236de68b9e7cb41336972a21b60ebcf","category":"Cycling"}